title: This Is What Investors Are Getting Wrong About Facebook's Cryptocurrency
text: Facebook's Libra , a global payments system based on cryptocurrency, was unveiled June 18. When it launches next year, the gated community of 2 billion will soon have its own currency.

title: Better Buy: Facebook, Inc. vs. Twitter, Inc.
text: Two of the most popular social media stocks out there have very different stories, and one is a more enticing buy.
